  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817470/extras/8c33dc41208699da53e816849df995a1.avif?t=1521546882\" width=568 height=385 /></span><br>In the game <strong>ToaZZle</strong> You have to go through 40 interesting levels of puzzle, <br>which would leave only the red frog on a water lilies. <br>Jump from water lilies to water lilies as fast and deftly as you can,<br>trying not to get into the pond, but pushing others there! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817470/extras/82333c19f6138d369bf495006a46f804.avif?t=1521546882\" width=402 height=321 /></span><br><br>Sounds simple, doesn't it? It's easy to check. <br>Start <strong>ToaZZle</strong> right now and start passing levels <br>as fast as possible to get 3 stars and achievements! <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/817470/extras/cfe09163632b793f48a3d89b53e1c790.avif?t=1521546882\" width=560 height=389 /></span><br><br>Show everyone who is the king of the pond! <br><br><strong>Peculiar properties: <br>- Beautiful graphics <br>- Challenging and interesting levels <br>- Pleasant soundtrack <br>- Achievements</strong>",
